{"tid":761738,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本將用190億港元購入2套「陸基神盾」防衛日本全境   料2023年完成部署","createTime":"2018-07-30T15:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T16:43:25.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"042b802160d57bd3300a50362402e8c9fac6848c","tid":761738,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:39:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180730/58505026\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180730%2F58505026&d=ryHwDdLHKbljfyhePtXIWrDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=7a4750a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180730%2F58505026&h=a4de2782\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180730/58505026</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180730/large/1532957402_a17f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180730%2Flarge%2F1532957402_a17f.jpg&h=ae3c8716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本防衛大臣小野寺五典周一表示，日本政府已經計劃在2023年度完成「陸基神盾」反導系統的部署，每套系統價值1,340億日元（約95億港元），政府已經決定購入兩套。<br />\n<br />\n小野寺引述美方提議指，從雙方簽約後到成功部署第一套「陸基神盾」需要約6年時間，日方引入的「陸基神盾」反導系統將搭載洛歇馬丁公司研發的最新型雷達「LMSSR」。據稱，「LMSSR」的探測距離是日本海上自衛隊在神盾艦搭載的「SPY1」雷達的2倍以上。<br />\n<br />\n雖然北韓核危機近月有降溫迹象，但小野寺稱「北韓的威脅沒有改變。不掌握（北韓）邁向棄核的動向」，強調部署「陸基神盾」是有必要。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，日本政府認為只須部署兩套「陸基神盾」就能防衛日本全境，目前當局把陸上自衛隊分別位於秋田市和山口縣萩市的練習場，作為部署候選地。<br />\n<br />\n共同社／日本新聞網"},{"pid":"91188b7867f710641b3b9dc73283f7731f4616a2","tid":761738,"uid":94828,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:42:41.000Z","msg":"高鐵三跑港珠澳啲錢唔知防衛到幾個香港呢"},{"pid":"0e303b1bea6a776dc1373d8767fe37d42bd04065","tid":761738,"uid":3936,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"91188b7867f710641b3b9dc73283f7731f4616a2","tid":7617